    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Arboridia koreana sp. nov.: 1. Habitus. 3. Head. 5. Face. 7. Forewing. Arboridia septempunctata sp. nov.: 2. Habitus. 4. Head. 6. Face. 8. Forewing. Scales: 0.5 mm" ;
